## Relationship to Security Account

The management account and security account work together but have clearly separated responsibilities:

| Responsibility | Management Account | Security Account |
|---|---|---|
| Register delegated admins | Yes | No |
| Enable trusted access | Yes | No |
| Manage SCPs | Yes | No |
| Manage OU structure | Yes | No |
| Operate Config aggregator | No | Yes |
| Deploy conformance packs | No | Yes |
| Triage GuardDuty findings | No | Yes |
| Manage Security Hub dashboard | No | Yes |
| Deploy security-account infra | No | Yes |

Both accounts are deployed via separate Terraform configurations in the same or separate GitHub repositories. Changes to delegation or SCPs in the management account can impact the security account — coordinate changes between the two.

